## Is Public Domain

> Check if a domain is public

## Screenshot

<img src="https://gitlab.com/yoginth/ispublicdomain/raw/master/Screenshot.png" width="550">

## Install

```
$ pip install ispublicdomain
```

## Usage

```python
import ispublicdomain as domain

domain.check('http://google.com')
#=> True
```
